### ============================================
### 🧪 TEST AUDIT LOGS API - SuperMarketMini
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = 
@managerToken = 

### ============================================
### 🔐 1. LOGIN (Chạy trước để lấy token)
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login Admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 1.2 Login Manager
# @name loginManager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "manager",
  "password": "Manager@123"
}

### ============================================
### 📋 2. GET ALL AUDIT LOGS
### ============================================

### 2.1 Admin - Get All Audit Logs (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.2 Admin - Get Audit Logs with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.3 Admin - Filter by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs?userId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.4 Admin - Filter by Action
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs?action=CREATE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.5 Admin - Filter by Table Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs?tableName=Products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.6 Admin - Filter by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2.7 Manager - Get Audit Logs (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 2.8 No Token - Get Audit Logs (Expected: 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs

### ============================================
### 🔍 3. GET AUDIT LOG BY ID
### ============================================

### 3.1 Admin - Get Audit Log by ID (Expected: 200 OK or 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3.2 Manager - Get Audit Log by ID (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 3.3 Admin - Get Non-existent Audit Log (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 👤 4. GET AUDIT LOGS BY USER
### ============================================

### 4.1 Admin - Get Logs by User (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.2 Admin - Get Logs by User with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/user/1?fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4.3 Manager - Get Logs by User (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/user/2
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 4.4 Admin - Get Logs by Non-existent User (Expected: 404 Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/user/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 📊 5. GET AUDIT LOGS BY TABLE
### ============================================

### 5.1 Admin - Get Logs by Table (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/table/Products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.2 Admin - Get Logs by Table with Record ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/table/Products?recordId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5.3 Manager - Get Logs by Table (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/table/Users
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 🏷️ 6. GET ACTION TYPES
### ============================================

### 6.1 Admin - Get All Action Types (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6.2 Manager - Get Action Types (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 📑 7. GET TABLE NAMES
### ============================================

### 7.1 Admin - Get All Table Names (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/tables
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7.2 Manager - Get Table Names (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/tables
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### ➕ 8. CREATE AUDIT LOG
### ============================================

### 8.1 Admin - Create Audit Log (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "action": "CREATE",
  "tableName": "TestTable",
  "recordId": 1,
  "oldValue": null,
  "newValue": "{\"name\": \"Test\"}",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1"
}

### 8.2 Admin - Create Audit Log without Action (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "tableName": "TestTable",
  "recordId": 1
}

### 8.3 Manager - Create Audit Log (Expected: 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

{
  "action": "UPDATE",
  "tableName": "Products",
  "recordId": 5
}

### ============================================
### 🗑️ 9. CLEANUP OLD AUDIT LOGS
### ============================================

### 9.1 Admin - Cleanup Logs Before Date (Expected: 200 OK)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/cleanup?beforeDate=2023-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.2 Admin - Cleanup Default (1 year ago) (Expected: 200 OK)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9.3 Manager - Cleanup Logs (Expected: 403 Forbidden)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 📈 10. GET STATISTICS
### ============================================

### 10.1 Admin - Get Statistics (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10.2 Manager - Get Statistics (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auditlogs/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 📝 HƯỚNG DẪN SỬ DỤNG
### ============================================
### 
### 1. Cài đặt VS Code extension "REST Client"
### 2. Chạy các request Login đầu tiên để lấy token
### 3. Copy token vào biến tương ứng
### 4. Chạy các request test theo thứ tự
###
